{"tid":2424401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[四叔]初選大搜捕︱提早報到同日「被辭職」 仁安護士學校校長：無怨無悔","createTime":"2021-02-26T14:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T02:07:49.000Z","uid":51271,"like":113,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e855c1e668ee0db6cdbbab268c46c4f4c1390637","tid":2424401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/MIYC5A3PCJHUDDMFGR44GWIVZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FMIYC5A3PCJHUDDMFGR44GWIVZU%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=6bf06093\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FMIYC5A3PCJHUDDMFGR44GWIVZU%2F&h=c86e7ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/MIYC5A3PCJHUDDMFGR44GWIVZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n多名參加「35+」初選的民主派人士，今天（26日）突然接獲警方通知提早至本周日（28日）報到，包括參加衞生服務界初選的袁偉傑。原是仁安醫院護士訓練學校校長的袁偉傑向《蘋果》表示，今午接獲醫院通知他「被辭職」 及須同日離職。<br />\n<br />\n對於須要突然離開工作了4年的醫院，袁稱感到詫異，但亦理解院方決定，「對醫院無恨、無嬲」。仁安醫院由「四叔」李兆基家族的恒基兆業全資擁有，其長子李家傑現時是全國政協委員。"},{"pid":"0b4cb197d6d670c7f1a3a35c1c39d017fe612c25","tid":2424401,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbc7a97b4a55fe6f561bd3fbf82563379029333","tid":2424401,"uid":186,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"仁安醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.